$\left(\sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}\right)^{3} = \binom{3}{0}(\sqrt{2})^{3} + \binom{3}{1}(\sqrt{2})^{2}(\sqrt{3})+\binom{3}{2}(\sqrt{2})(\sqrt{3})^{2}
